{"tid":141810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"青年介紹低智女賣淫獲撤控　官嘆脫罪非無辜","createTime":"2017-03-03T08:29:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T01:05:03.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ee8c9e868ccdabf6b0b30261b45cfb146d644127","tid":141810,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/03/162825_ed518da919808280588f41d0d8cb5397.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F03%2F162825_ed518da919808280588f41d0d8cb5397.jpg&h=d1953d36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n智商接近輕度智障的17歲女學生，為錢出賣肉體淪為妓女，最終她完成性交易後，擔心懷孕向社工呻苦，始揭發其慘痛經歷，她的18歲男舊中學同窗被指向她介紹嫖客，因而惹上官非。該名男同窗早前被控一項促致年齡在21歲以下的女童與人非法性交罪，案件原定今在九龍城法院開審，但控方向法庭表示，事主受精神問題困擾，不願出庭作供，最終決定撤控。 <br />\n<br />\n被告張晉燁被控於2015年11月22日在何文田邨一單位，促使當時17歲的女事主X與一名麥姓男子非法性交。 <br />\n<br />\n暫委裁判官梁禮賢庭上詢問撤控原因，控方解釋，X的智商雖只得74，但法律上智商低至72才會被列為「精神上無行為能力的人」。控方指X本身亦有精神問題，受事件影響感到極大困擾，警方有跟她落口供，但她表示不願出庭頂證被告，要她出庭會接受不到。辯方則指，根據X口供，是X主動要求被告「介紹男仔畀佢識」，辯方最後放棄申請訟費。 <br />\n<br />\n梁官散庭前特別告誡被告，指其脫罪只因技術及法律問題，以及與事主心理質素有關。梁官怒斥：「你好彩！你同佢係舊同學，你心知肚明人哋智商只係得70幾，仲叫人做啲咁嘅嘢？」梁官重申：「你係好彩，唔係你無辜！」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170303/mobile/bkn-20170303125552641-0303_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170303%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170303125552641-0303_00822_001.html&d=bDHmYwogulq9FkNLxWxOthv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=ee0ead09\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170303/mobile/bkn-20170303125552641-0303_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b03ee5f11c27c95a8a82adf0fecdb334eb280086","tid":141810,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:29:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e08d078861f45e3cb5f7f58f1094922812e55b11","tid":141810,"uid":86851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa2bfdc22c8b5e17b17f34326ac873372133d88c","tid":141810,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:31:46.000Z","msg":"相由心生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed767a456f3293ea5204ffc2020951eaa6829931","tid":141810,"uid":59181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:32:19.000Z","msg":"成個大陸仔咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"415a6d803b1468e78c0e7daa5863ee17c5013ef3","tid":141810,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:33:43.000Z","msg":"係網絡世界<br />\n好似冇好彩呢回事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0c3c03e78f02d55f8a704a9fc429722bcef01d","tid":141810,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:33:44.000Z","msg":"唔係話幫條友仔講說話<br />\n但係個官咁樣加個人意見有冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0122eda6f6937dfc151924b9531fba7967d6f843","tid":141810,"uid":39921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:34:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係話幫條友仔講說話<br />\n但係個官咁樣加個人意見有冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n結案陳詞姐，其實更彰顯到真正司法獨立"},{"pid":"2125776b352cb17c5db31cd89166f83279f585a8","tid":141810,"uid":6520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:39:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係話幫條友仔講說話<br />\n但係個官咁樣加個人意見有冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n結案陳詞姐，其實更彰顯到真正司法獨立</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"734ccab0a0933527959631d6a738f9491c0a127f","tid":141810,"uid":2135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:40:24.000Z","msg":"仆街死啦"},{"pid":"005dad18422e01bae74404a4af50387ac802dc57","tid":141810,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:40:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係話幫條友仔講說話<br />\n但係個官咁樣加個人意見有冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n結案陳詞姐，其實更彰顯到真正司法獨立</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正解！<br />\n判案靠理據案例，官用專業知識同跟足法律程序判，但唔代表法官/大眾既睇法同結果相同。<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得個官講得好啱~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6056524be9aa24bdc5784b0581fee7c5a3af3b61","tid":141810,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:41:23.000Z","msg":"個被告成個前野咁"},{"pid":"a0a6d2b58db06f11cc179a563e7a2ab088d18537","tid":141810,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:42:58.000Z","msg":"辯方則指，根據X口供，是X主動要求被告「介紹男仔畀佢識」，辯方最後放棄申請訟費。 <br />\n<br />\n我唔覺得個女仔值得同情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e423a5cf2c16407ea4d4e27cf7ef7bd466a06603","tid":141810,"uid":4545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:43:02.000Z","msg":"佢個樣好陰濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0738ee941340555e5a30484435e596456650d788","tid":141810,"uid":23106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:43:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個被告成個前野咁</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a019707246cdf52621003fea9cdb815cfd4688","tid":141810,"uid":88101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:43:43.000Z","msg":"<blockqu